Package org.risk.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllTests
    The Class act as test suite for all the test classes
    Constants
    This Class Stores all the constant values for countryID and Colors etc.
    Continent
    The Instance of this class represents continent.
    ContinentTest
    The test class for Continent class which test the addState method
    Country
    An instance of this class represents a country, which will act as a player in the game.
    CountryTest
    The test class for Country class which test the getMyStateList method
    GameEngine
    The Instance of this Class holds Map Object.
    GameEngineTest
    The test class for GameEngine class which test its various methods
    Item
    The instance of this Class is used to hold the id and name for State, Continent, etc.
    Link
    An instance of this class represent a connection between two states.
    LinkTest
    The test class for Link class which test the getSourceState and getDestintionState method
    Logger
    The Class is used to maintain the log of the game.
    Map
    An instance of this class represent a map.
    MapLoader
    An instance of this class gets the XML from the controller and converts it to Map object by calling related methods.
    MapLoaderTest
    Test class for MapSaver Class which will test whether map object is being loaded
    MapSaver
    An instance of this class gets the path from the controller and converts the map object to XML by calling related methods.
    MapSaverTest
    Test class for MapSaver Class which will test whether map object is being saved
    MapTest
    The test class for Map class which test the MapValidation addState and addContinent method
    MapVisualization
    This Class is used to Create the map on the screen using JUNG Class Library
    Resource
    The class hold the instance of the Resource.
    State
    This class represents states of the map
    StateTest
    The test class for State class which test the setIsCapital method
    Technology
    The class hold the instance of Technology.
